      "content": "hey im having a really bad headache right now... like honestly the worst one i've ever had in my life. and i noticed my left eye looks a bit weird like the side of my face is slightly drooping? i get migraines sometimes when i'm stressed so i'm assuming its just a really bad one. any idea what i should do to help the pain go away?",
